        <div class="form-group col-12">
            <span>備註 Remarks:</span>
            <ol>
                <li>如有需要，可自行影印表格<br>Applicants can make copy of the form if needed.</li>
                <li>每張報名表只可報<u>一個</u>組別<br>An application form can be applied for <u>one</u> category only.</li>
            </ol>
            <br>
        </div>

        <!-- 費用 Fee -->
        <div class="form-group col-12">
            <h5 class="labelHead">費用 Fee</h5>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>團體項目 Group Event: $250 X </label>
                <input id="teamNo" type="number" name="TRGP[TeamNumber]" value="1" style="width: 25pt;"
                    required readonly <% if (req.session.TRGPdata != null) {%> value="<%= req.session.TRGPdata.teamNo%>" <%}%>>
                <span>隊 team(s) = $</span>
                <input id="teamPrice" type="number" name="TRGP[TeamPrice]" value="250" readonly required 
                <% if (req.session.TRGPdata != null) {%> value="<%= req.session.TRGPdata.teamPrice%>" <%}%>>
                <br>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>總額 Total price = $</label> 
                <input id="total" type="number" name="TRGP[TeamTotalPrice]" value="250" readonly required 
                <% if (req.session.TRGPdata != null) {%> value="<%= req.session.TRGPdata.total%>"<%}%>>

            </div>

            <span style="font-style: italic;">*請以支票付款，並以郵寄方式或親臨辦公室遞交支票<br>Please make payment by cheque and submit it by
